            <abstract><p>Encloses two rare fungi he recently found [extant]: 'Xyloma pini' and 'Trichia reticulata', observations on his finding them. Thanks Smith for offer to send ferns; directions for sending. Will be glad to hear when the fourth part of "Flora Britannica" is published.</p><p>Two specimens, labelled, "'Trichia reticulata'" and "'Xyloma pini' Messrs de Albertini &amp; de Schweiniz" [attached to JES/COR/26/26].</p></abstract>
